    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Fajar Surya Wisesa Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture and sale of packaging papers in Indonesia and other Asian countries. It offers coated duplex boards for use in light-weight packaging materials of pharmaceutical products, shoes, household goods, processed foods, and consumer electronics. The company also provides container board products, such as brown packaging paper that is used for the outer layers of corrugated sheets; fluting paper for the construction of carton boxes; and white liner board for industrial packaging and box making. It sells its products directly to industrial and consumer goods manufacturing companies. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Jakarta Pusat, Indonesia. PT Fajar Surya Wisesa Tbk  operates as a subsidiary of Scgp Solutions (Singapore) Pte Ltd.",
